{
  "stem": "4160.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where are we going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where are we going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw a [NON-ENGLISH]-- a well with water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we run to that well, and we pulled out the water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We pulled out the water from this, and we start to drink.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then next to the well was a little house, that was about 15 policemans, Ukrainish policemans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, they know that in the woods are some hiding Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were sitting in that little house and as soon as we start to drink the water, we're all surrounded with police.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Me and him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Me and Indja Benderski.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Surrounded.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, one way we could run-- we was-- we have no shoes-- excuse me-- no shoes, nothing, hungry, thirsty, wet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't recognize each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they started surrounded us, and we run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We run to the woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He run faster than me did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Indja Benderski run faster me and they caught me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They-- the policeman, they caught me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they didn't hurt me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they took me, and Indja Benderski run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He run away and they caught me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They caught me right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They couldn't kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If they would kill me right away, they wouldn't receive a [INAUDIBLE] sugar, or [INAUDIBLE] salt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They wouldn't have the prizes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they have to take me to the city Klevan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "First, they took me to Zukow, to that-- to that village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was about 3 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They laid me down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put me on my hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they this and that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they sometimes an Ukraini came in and kicked me in the this, and kick me here, kick me there, but I didn't pay attention for that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
